OUTPUT Menu window
OUTPUT Commerce button, English button, Physics button
INPUT Press the button

IF English button is pressed
	THEN
	    INITIALIZE points to 0
	    OUTPUT submit button
	    OUTPUT radio buttons
	    STORE questions with variants of answers in questionsArray
    	STORE answers in answersArray
    	INITIALIZE index to 1
    	PRINT question with index "index"
    	REPLACE the radio buttons' text with variants of answers to the question with the index "index"

    	INPUT Press the submit button



		OUTPUT English quiz window

	ELSE

		IF Commerce button is pressed
			THEN
				OUTPUT Commerce quiz window
			ELSE

				IF Physics button is pressed
					THEN
						OUTPUT Commerce quiz window
